{"id":10926,"date":"2018-10-09T12:40:23","date_gmt":"2018-10-09T07:10:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=10926"},"modified":"2019-04-02T19:09:28","modified_gmt":"2019-04-02T13:39:28","slug":"laxmi-agarwal","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/laxmi-agarwal\/","title":{"rendered":"Laxmi Agarwal Wiki, Age, Boyfriend, Children, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-10942\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-Picture.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal\" width=\"481\" height=\"481\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-Picture.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-Picture-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-Picture-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-Picture-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 481px) 100vw, 481px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Laxmi Agarwal is an <strong>activist<\/strong> who became a victim of an <strong>acid attack<\/strong> at the tender of 15. Let us take a dig into Laxmi&#8217;s struggle to survive and her unbreakable approach towards life after an acid attack.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce31b457bb\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce31b457bb\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/laxmi-agarwal\/#BiographyWiki\" title=\"Biography\/Wiki\">Biography\/Wiki<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/laxmi-agarwal\/#Boyfriend_Children_Family\" title=\"Boyfriend, Children &amp; Family\">Boyfriend, Children &amp; Family<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/laxmi-agarwal\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/laxmi-agarwal\/#Facts\" title=\"Facts\">Facts<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BiographyWiki\"><\/span><span id=\"BiographyWiki\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"color: #800080;\">Biography\/Wiki<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Laxmi was born on <strong>1 June 1990<\/strong>, in <strong>New Delhi<\/strong>. This <strong>28<\/strong>-year-old strong woman is a pure example for all the acid attack survivors across the world. In <strong>2005<\/strong>, 15-year-old Laxmi was attacked by a 32-year-old man,\u00a0<strong>Gudda<\/strong> a.k.a <strong>Nahim Khan<\/strong> and his 2 other friends <strong>for rejecting his marriage proposal<\/strong>. Guddu was Laxmi&#8217;s friend&#8217;s elder brother.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10943\" style=\"width: 247px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10943\" class=\" wp-image-10943\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-before-acid-attack.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal before acid attack\" width=\"237\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-before-acid-attack.jpg 481w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-before-acid-attack-180x300.jpg 180w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 237px) 100vw, 237px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10943\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laxmi Agarwal before the acid attack<\/p><\/div>\n<p>The acid attack disfigured her face, her back, and many other parts of her body. Just after her recovery, she came out of her home to campaign for \u2018<strong>Stop Acid Attacks<\/strong>\u2019 and worked as a campaign coordinator and also filed a <strong>PIL<\/strong> in which she pleaded for a <strong>total ban<\/strong> on the sale of acid, citing the expanding number of incidents of acid attacks on women in 2006. After some time, she coined her own campaign,\u00a0\u2018<strong>StopSaleAcid<\/strong>,\u2019 for which she was awarded\u00a0many awards and honours.<\/p>\n<div class=\"flex-video flex-video-youtube\"><iframe width=\"1060\" height=\"596\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/yK6tQmocmcY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/div>\n<p>Her work made her the voice of\u00a0all the acid attack survivors across the world. She along with other acid attack victims started a\u00a0hunger strike for the rehabilitation of such survivors\u00a0and also to achieve an immediate legal justice. In 2013, the Supreme Court regulated a new set of rules prevailing the sale of acid in India in which a person below the age of 18 could not purchase acids and an identity card should be produced by the customer before purchasing acid.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Boyfriend_Children_Family\"><\/span><span id=\"Family_Boyfriend\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"color: #800080;\"><span id=\"Family_Caste_Boyfriend\" class=\"ez-toc-section\">Boyfriend, Children &amp; Family<\/span><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Laxmi was born into a middle-class family. Her father was a <strong>domestic cook<\/strong> and her mother was a <strong>homemaker<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10944\" style=\"width: 454px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10944\" class=\" wp-image-10944\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-mother.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal with her mother\" width=\"444\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-mother.jpg 637w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-mother-300x283.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 444px) 100vw, 444px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10944\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laxmi Agarwal with her mother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In an interview,\u00a0Laxmi stated that her father was her greatest pillar of strength. Her father and her brother passed away due to a prolonged disease. She met her love, <strong>Alok Dixit<\/strong> during a campaign. The couple decided to move in together without getting married, challenging all the taboos of the Indian society. They together have a daughter, Pihu. However, the couple split soon after the birth of their daughter.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10945\" style=\"width: 553px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10945\" class=\" wp-image-10945\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-partner-Alok-and-daughter-Pihu.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal with her partner, Alok and daughter, Pihu\" width=\"543\" height=\"397\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-partner-Alok-and-daughter-Pihu.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-partner-Alok-and-daughter-Pihu-300x219.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-partner-Alok-and-daughter-Pihu-768x562.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 543px) 100vw, 543px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10945\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laxmi Agarwal with her partner, Alok, and daughter, Pihu<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span id=\"Career\" class=\"ez-toc-section\" style=\"color: #800080;\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Laxmi completed her class <strong>10th<\/strong> from <strong>Sarvodaya Kanya Vidyalaya<\/strong> school. She had to stop her further studies after the awful accident. In 2014,\u00a0she started <strong>hosting<\/strong>\u00a0a television show,\u00a0<strong>Udaan<\/strong>, airing on New Express.\u00a0Laxmi along with her partner, Alok, founded an NGO, <strong>Chhanv Foundation.<\/strong> She also became the face of the brand, \u2018<strong>Viva n Diva campaign<\/strong>.\u2019<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10946\" style=\"width: 588px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10946\" class=\" wp-image-10946\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-the-face-of-Viva-n-Diva-Campaign.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal, the face of Viva n Diva Campaign\" width=\"578\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-the-face-of-Viva-n-Diva-Campaign.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-the-face-of-Viva-n-Diva-Campaign-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-the-face-of-Viva-n-Diva-Campaign-768x461.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 578px) 100vw, 578px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10946\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laxmi Agarwal, the face of Viva n Diva Campaign<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In 2014, Laxmi was honored with the <strong>International Women of Courage Award<\/strong> presented by the First Lady,\u00a0<strong>Michelle Obama<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10950\" style=\"width: 542px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10950\" class=\" wp-image-10950\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-Michelle-Obama.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal with Michelle Obama\" width=\"532\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-Michelle-Obama.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-Michelle-Obama-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-Michelle-Obama-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10950\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laxmi Agarwal with Michelle Obama<\/p><\/div>\n<p>Laxmi walked the ramp\u00a0at London Fashion Week in 2016.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10947\" style=\"width: 456px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10947\" class=\" wp-image-10947\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-at-London-Fashion-Week-2016.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal at London Fashion Week 2016\" width=\"446\" height=\"378\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-at-London-Fashion-Week-2016.jpg 708w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-at-London-Fashion-Week-2016-300x254.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 446px) 100vw, 446px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10947\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laxmi Agarwal at London Fashion Week 2016<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Facts\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\">Facts<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Laxmi always wanted to become either a singer or a dancer since her childhood. She also told that she was going to attend her first ever singing class, the day she was attacked by &#8216;Guddu.&#8217;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She also revealed that she was very scared when her daughter was born. She thought her daughter would get scared on seeing her.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_10948\" style=\"width: 351px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10948\" class=\" wp-image-10948\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-Daughter-Pihu.jpg\" alt=\"Laxmi Agarwal with her Daughter, Pihu\" width=\"341\" height=\"432\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-Daughter-Pihu.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/10\/Laxmi-Agarwal-with-her-Daughter-Pihu-237x300.jpg 237w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 341px) 100vw, 341px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-10948\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Laxmi Agarwal with her Daughter, Pihu<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2018, Laxmi disclosed in an interview that she faces a great difficulty in finding a job which could fulfill her and her daughter&#8217;s basic needs of life. She revealed that she is an experienced beautician but her disfigured face hampers all the job opportunities she gets.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2018,<strong>\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/deepika-padukone\/\">Deepika Padukone<\/a><\/strong>\u00a0was signed to play the role of Laxmi in her <strong>biopic<\/strong> and also turned producer with the film in collaboration with the director,\u00a0<strong>Meghna Gulzar<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Laxmi Agarwal is an activist who became a victim of an acid attack at the tender of 15. Let us take a dig into Laxmi&#8217;s struggle to survive and her unbreakable approach towards life after an acid attack. Biography\/Wiki Laxmi was born on 1 June 1990, in New Delhi. This 28-year-old strong woman is a pure example for all the acid attack survivors across the world. In 2005, 15-year-old Laxmi was attacked by a 32-year-old man,\u00a0Gudda a.k.a Nahim Khan and his 2 other friends for rejecting his marriage proposal. Guddu was Laxmi&#8217;s friend&#8217;s elder brother. The acid attack disfigured her <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":10942,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[2,1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10926"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/17"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=10926"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10926\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":20788,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/10926\/revisions\/20788"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/10942"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=10926"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=10926"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=10926"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}